    {
      "title": "[正面] Delve into a world of unexplainable horrors and in...",
      "summary": "Delve into a world of unexplainable horrors and investigate the mysteries behind the world post-Dissolution, you are expected to experience engaging, in-depth rogue-lite card battle gameplay, with beautiful and unique art, all of these are put into a heartfelt story of ups and downs. The gacha system is quite generous, but can still be cruel because of the pity being after getting 2 non-rate up characters/cards. With that said, for the first 7 hours into the game, I was very immersed and invested in the game, the combat system, and the lore inspired by Lovecraftian works. I will continue playing on the mobile version, too.",
